ch tools. This includes Merrill Lynch/Bank of America’s internal equity research that ranks equities on volatility, potential return and dividend security. Third-party screening through Recognia provides recommendations and technical analysis on stocks and other securities. Trefis is a third-party tool that allows you to break down a company’s revenue and expenses into components to see where a company makes money. You can then manipulate these numbers to make estimates about a how company’s stock’s price might be affected by those changes. These tools are useful for investors of all skill levels.","The Merrill Edge mobile trading app is a useful tool for managing accounts and placing trades when you’re away from the main platform. You can set up alerts and research potential investments from the app. Research tools include analyst research and reports. The one drawback of the mobile app is that trading is limited.","This broker also offers an advanced platform called Market Pro. To use this you’ll need to maintain a minimum balance of $50,000 and make at least three trades a month. MarketPro includes advanced tools to help traders enter orders more quickly and is well suited for options traders especially."]},"id":"1c4982e4-f2ea-4970-8344-9ac4c656db15","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/HRkb4heUo58t96Up7ySEb3.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"The cost to trade stocks and ETFs is $6.95, which is well within the industry average. Options trades have that same base fee, but also a per-contract fee of $0.75. The cost to buy into a mutual fund is $19.95, which is much lower than many of the more prominent brokerages.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/1624-merrill-lynch6.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/HRkb4heUo58t96Up7ySEb3.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"HRkb4heUo58t96Up7ySEb3","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/HRkb4heUo58t96Up7ySEb3.jpg","alt":""},"id":"07319bc6-fe49-4e90-ba5e-e0fa382a82c1","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Merrill Edge doesn’t offer any commission-free ETFs. You don’t need a minimum balance to start investing, though as mentioned above, if you want to use the Market Pro platform you’ll need to meet account and trade frequency minimums."]},"id":"cda0f3c5-cc31-4d73-97f4-2c9b4aec624f","type":"text"},{"data":{"path":"/qNz5oMAxFkW6meCvtFvdEP.jpg","link":{"href":"","rel":null,"target":""},"caption":"This trading platform has some of the most expansive and useful educational resources of the brokers we reviewed. Investors of all skill levels can find something useful in the Investor Education section of the platform. If you’re new to investing, you can learn how to prioritize your financial goals and find investments to meet your needs.","fullscreen":true,"importSrc":"http://www.toptenreviews.com/i/rev/scrn/small/1624-merrill-lynch11.jpg","src":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qNz5oMAxFkW6meCvtFvdEP.jpg","credit":"","align":"","id":"qNz5oMAxFkW6meCvtFvdEP","mos":"https://dev.mos.cms.futurecdn.net/qNz5oMAxFkW6meCvtFvdEP.jpg","alt":""},"id":"f9435846-b4a1-49e5-a4ff-34100174e64f","type":"image"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Intermediate to advanced investors can take advantage of videos and regularly scheduled webinars about trading strategies, market movements and other investing tools. One advantage of a broker that is integrated with a bank is that the information covers more than just investing – you can find a wide range of information about personal finance. This is one of the standout features of this broker.","Merrill Edge is an excellent choice for investors of all levels. Beginners can make use of the education resources, low trading costs and screening tools. Advanced traders can make use of the MarketPro platform, which enables advanced analysis and quick orders."]},"id":"248c0f3e-805a-4cd9-ac42-7c4189b60822","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_1641","url":"/merrill-lynch-review","authors":[{"e